---
title: Governing ecological connectivity in cross-scale dependent systems
collection: publications
permalink: /publication/2022-BioScience
excerpt: 'Ecosystem management and governance of cross-scale dependent systems require integrating knowledge about ecological connectivity in its multiple forms and scales.'
date: 2022-01-25
venue: 'BioScience'
paperurl: 'https://doi.org/10.1093/biosci/biab140'
citation: 'Keeley et al. (2022). Governing ecological connectivity in cross-scale dependent systems.; <i>BioScience</i>. Advance Article.'
---
This paper discusses the need for governance to accomodate the interdependency of ecosystems with specific examples from
a major estuary in California, USA.
E-mail atstahl@wsu.edu or go to ResearchGate (https://www.researchgate.net/profile/Amanda-Stahl-4/research) to request the full-text article.
